"images/article/115544rew234/11.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		<p>14）修改此数值<em>alter system set log_archive_min_succeed_dest=2;</em></p>\r\n                                                		  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/12.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		<p>（注：如果既设置了mandatory参数，有设置了最少成功数。两个都必须满足）</p>\r\n														<p>15）修改归档日志状态为禁止（defer）<em>alter system set log_archive_dest_state_1=defer;</em></p>\r\n														<p>16）查看<em>select dest_name,status,binding,process,error from v$archive_dest where status not like \'INA%\';</em></p>\r\n														\r\n                                                		  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/13.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/14.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		<p>17）修改其为可用<em>alter system set log_archive_dest_state_1=enable;</em></p>\r\n														<p>18）查看<em>select dest_name,status,binding,process,error from v$archive_dest where status not like \'INA%\';</em></p>\r\n                                                		\r\n                                                          <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/15.png\"   ></p>\r\n														  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/16.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		<p>19）设置备用目录我们先设置一个终点目录。</p>\r\n														<p><em>alter system set log_archive_dest_4=\'location=e:\\app\\teacher\\log4\\\';</em></p>\r\n														<p>修改log_archive_dest_1的参数，设置log_archive_dest_4作为备用归档目录</p>\r\n														<p><em>alter system set log_archive_dest_1=\'location=e:\\app\\teacher\\log1\\ mandatory alternate=log_archive_dest_4\';</em></p>\r\n														<p>更改log_archive_dest_4状态为alternate.\r\n														<p><em>alter system set log_archive_dest_state_4=alternate;</em></p>\r\n														<p>然后我们查看一下log_archive_dest_1</p>\r\n														<p><em>show parameter log_archive_dest_1;</em></p>\r\n                                                		  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/17.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		<p>然后在查看下所有的归档终点名称和状态：<em>select dest_name,status,binding,process,error from v$archive_dest where status not like \'INA%\'; </em></p>\r\n                                                		  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/18.png\"   ></p>\r\n                                                		  <p class=\"img\"><img   alt=\"控制文件\" src=\"images/article/115544rew234/19.png\"   ></p>\r\n														<p>我们这里看到设置成功。</p>\r\n                                                		<p class=\"notice\">\r\n                                                			<a href=\"http://us-forever.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%BD%92%E6%A1%A3%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97.docx\">文档下载</a>\r\n                                                		</p>');
